        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Congressional First Class Flights Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits funds provided for the official travel expenses of a Member of Congress from being used for airline accommodations that are not coach-class, unless the accommodations are necessary to accommodate a medical disability or other special need.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
